name: AWR-S02-MIRR Control unit for Parabolic mirror
description:
AWR-S02-MIRR:
A special control unit for Parabolic Mirror that can control 1 projector, up to 4 ASS-01 sensors and up to 4 light beacons. 
Projector in default is 100W (ALP-AC-100-S) blinking.
Also master-slave connection is ready in default HW and FW.

AWR-S02-MIRR keeps all beacons green and projector is off, when any ASS-01 detect vehicle / human / vehicle and human from one direction, beacon of this direction turns red and projector starts blinking. After end of detection and ASS-01 timesout, projector is turned off and beacon of that direction turns back to green.

Settings for detection of vehicles / humans / vehicles and humans is done by HW configuration and is possible to choose type of detection for each ASS-01 separately (for each direction).

There is no possibility to react differently to detection from one ASS-01 (from one direction) by two different projector effects.
For example, it is not possible to flash projector when detecting a forklift from one direction and pulse projector when detecting a pedestrian from the same direction.
Projector effect is only one (blinking as default).

When detection comes from multiple ASS-01 sensors in same time, 
beacon of each detected direction is red, until end of detection from this direction and timedout.
When detection comes from multiple ASS-01 sensors in same time, projector continues on, until no ASS-01 is activated. 

There is also possible to start projection just in case of detection from multiple directions in the same time - detection form just one direction should be interpreted just by red beacon in this direction.

name: AWR-S Simple relay
description:
Simple relay control unit for triggering on/off the projector.
Turn on the projector when input 5 - 40V DC is present.
Control just one projector with no effects, just simple on/off. AWR-S is compatible with all projectors in portfolio (2.2024).
Does not need a time to boot, reacts immediately.
description_en: Simple relay for triggering on/off the projector.

description_en:
Infrared sensor with a long detection distance and has less interference by visible light. The implementations of modulated IR signal immune the sensor to the interferences caused by the normal light of a light bulb or the sun light. This sensor has a screwdriver adjustment to set the appropriate detected distance to make it useful in many applications, and then gives a digital output when it senses something within that range. This sensor does not measure a distance value. It can be used for collision avoidance robot and machine automation. The sensor provides a non-contact detection.

Specifications
•	Input voltage : +24V DC
•	Current consumption : > 25mA (min) ~ 100mA (max)
•	Dimension : 1.7cm (diameter) x 4.5cm (length)
•	Cable length : 45cm
•	Detection of objects : transparent or opaque
•	Diffuse reflective type
•	Sensing range : 3cm to 80cm (depends on obstacle surface)
•	NPN output (normally high)
•	Environment temperature : -25 °C ~ 55 °C

name: ASS-09 Optosensor - reflective sensor 1 - 450 mm
description:
U reflexních snímačů (stejně jako u reflexních
závor) jsou vysílač a přijímač umístěny v
jednom pouzdře. Vyhodnocováno není ale
přerušení světelných paprsků, ale odraz od
snímaného objektu. K detekci objektu je třeba
odraz dostatečného množství světla zpět
k přijímači. Spínací vzdálenost reflexních
snímačů závisí ve značné míře na reflexních
schopnostech snímaného předmětu.
description_en:
For reflective sensors (as well as reflective
barrier) the transmitter and receiver are located in
one case. However, it is not evaluated
interruption of light rays, but reflection from
the scanned object. To detect the object, you need
reflecting enough light back
to the receiver. Reflective switching distance
of sensors depends to a large extent on reflective ones
capabilities of the scanned object.

name: DEMO-KIT-S
description:
1x ALP-AC-100-S-20 – 100 W projector with active cooling and 20 degrees optic
1x SLP-PG-2C-S - symbol - Warning forklift
1x AWR-03A – Zone reader (reacts to the personal tag)
1x ASA-22 – Optical LED warning
1x AWL-07-AS personal wrist tag with silicone strap

Funkce:
Demokit má 3 zóny, čemuž odpovídá barevná signalizace, vibrace WRISTu a spínání PJ:
SAFE: maják svítí zeleně, WRIST je v klidu, PJ nesvítí
WARNING: maják svítí oranžově, WRIST vibruje, PJ svítí
DANGER: maják svítí červeně, WRIST vibruje, PJ svítí
DRIVER: maják svítí červeně, WRIST nevibruje, PJ svítí
description_en:
1x ALP-AC-100-S-20 – 100 W projector with active cooling and 20 degrees optic
1x SLP-PG-2C-S - symbol - Warning forklift
1x AWR-03A – Zone reader (reacts to the personal tag)
1x ASA-22 – Optical LED warning
1x AWL-07-AS personal wrist tag with silicone strip

Function:
The demo kit has 3 zones, which correspond to beacon color, WRIST vibration and PJ projection:
SAFE: beacon lights green, WRIST doesnt vibrate, PJ is OFF
WARNING: beacon lights orange, WRIST vibrates, PJ is ON
DANGER: beacon lights red, WRIST vibrates, PJ is ON
DRIVER: beacon lights red, WRIST does not vibrate, PJ is ON
